@CalculatorApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5049

### Calculate expression (2 + 3 * 4 = 14)
POST {{CalculatorApi_HostAddress}}/api/calculator/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "operands": [2, 3, 4],
  "operators": ["+", "*"]
}

### Get memory value
GET {{CalculatorApi_HostAddress}}/api/calculator/memory
Accept: application/json

### Add value to memory
POST {{CalculatorApi_HostAddress}}/api/calculator/memory/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "value": 42
}

### Subtract value from memory
POST {{CalculatorApi_HostAddress}}/api/calculator/memory/subtract
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "value": 10
}

### Clear memory
POST {{CalculatorApi_HostAddress}}/api/calculator/memory/clear
